interpretation: The "cut of meat" card represents abundance and sustenance. It symbolizes the satisfaction of basic needs and desires, whether it be in the form of food, money, or other resources. This card reminds us to appreciate the abundance in our lives and to use it wisely. It can also signify indulgence and excess, warning us not to overindulge and become greedy. In a reading, this card may suggest material prosperity, success, and good fortune. It can also indicate a need to focus on practical matters and take care of one's physical well-being. Keywords associated with this card include nourishment, satisfaction, prosperity, indulgence, and practicality.
